column2: Table 9#3U# Gross Domestic Product and Final Sales of Software

column3: GDP less final sales of software
[Percent change from preceding period in chained (2009) dollar measures]:
GDP less final sales of software

column2: 1. Software estimates include own-account production and exclude software embedded in equipment.
2. Includes software classified as goods and excludes software classified as services.
3. Excludes services of software, measured by consumption of fixed capital, for general government.
